{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
For the reasons herein discussed, this Court has determined that Judgment based upon the stipulated facts must be entered in favor of the United States.
\par 
}
}
